                                                                                                                       7                                      Fan dies
                      
	London: A soccer fan died on Sunday after suffering a head injury and a heart attack in an incident during a Premier League match at Stoke City in central England, police said.         
	The 30-year-old man collapsed inside the Britannia Stadium on Saturday just after the half-time interval in the game between Stoke and Blackburn Rovers.         
	Police said they were investigating what led to the mans death.           (REUTERS)                                                                                                                 
